#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn15.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Dhītusutta "
msgstr "19. Daughter "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn15.19:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.19:1.2"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning. "

msgctxt "sn15.19:1.3"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ. "
msgstr "No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving. "

msgctxt "sn15.19:1.4"
msgid "Na so, bhikkhave, satto sulabharūpo yo na dhītābhūtapubbo iminā dīghena addhunā. "
msgstr "It’s not easy to find a sentient being who in all this long time has not previously been your daughter. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.19:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn15.19:1.6"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro. "
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. "

msgctxt "sn15.19:1.7"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ. "
msgstr "No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving. "

msgctxt "sn15.19:1.8"
msgid "Evaṃ dīgharattaṃ vo, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ tibbaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ byasanaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ, kaṭasī vaḍḍhitā. "
msgstr "For such a long time you have undergone suffering, agony, and disaster, swelling the cemeteries. "

msgctxt "sn15.19:1.9"
msgid "Yāvañcidaṃ, bhikkhave, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ, alaṃ virajjituṃ, alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. "
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.19:1.10"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

